.TH getfont  3 "R1c" "Silicon Graphics"
.SH NAME
.I getfont
- return the current raster font number
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.TP \w'FORTRAN\ \ \ 'u
C
.B "short getfont()"
.IP 
.TP \w'FORTRAN\ \ \ 'u
FORTRAN
.B "integer*2 function getfon()"
.IP 
.TP \w'FORTRAN\ \ \ 'u
Pascal
.B "function getfont: Short;"
.sp
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I Getfont
returns the index of the currently selected raster font.
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.I defrasterfont, font
.SH NOTE
This command can only be used in immediate mode.
